---
title: Thyme Chicken and Grape Pan Sauce with Caramelized Onions and Garlic Mashed Potatoes
description: Rich and flavourful thyme chicken gets a silky coating with a sticky blistered grape and onion pan sauce. Creamy garlicky mashed potatoes spruce up this chicken dinner!
